<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Simple Website</title>
  <style>
    /* Reset some default styles */
    body, ul {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    /* Page background and overall styling */
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f8f8f8;
    }

    /* Navbar styles */
    nav {
      background-color: #333;
      color: #fff;
      padding: 10px;
    }

    .navbar-container {
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .navbar-logo {
      font-size: 24px;
    }

    .navbar-menu {
      list-style: none;
    }

    .navbar-menu li {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-left: 20px;
    }

    .navbar-menu li:first-child {
      margin-left: 0;
    }

    .navbar-menu li a {
      color: #fff;
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 5px 10px;
      border-radius: 5px;
    }

    .navbar-menu li a:hover {
      background-color: #444;
    }

    .navbar-menu li a.active {
      font-weight: bold;
      background-color: #555;
    }

    /* Welcome message styles */
    .about-content {
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: 50px auto;
      text-align: center;
      background-color: #fff;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }

    .about-content h1 {
      font-size: 36px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .about-content p {
      font-size: 18px;
      color: #666;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <!-- Navbar -->
  <nav>
    <div class="navbar-container">
      <div class="navbar-logo">Authentication Demo</div>
      <ul class="navbar-menu">
        <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
        <li><a href="/contact">Contact</a></li>
        <li><a href="/about" class="active">About</a></li>
        <li>Welcome <%= name %></li>
        <li><a href="/logout">Logout</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <!-- Main Content - Welcome Message -->
  <div class="about-content">
    <h1>Our Company</h1>
    <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Nulla facilisi. Quisque eget felis ut ipsum accumsan laoreet. Fusce eu quam ut nisl suscipit scelerisque.</p>
    <p>Mauris euismod semper lacus, eget euismod quam facilisis id. Sed facilisis nisi quis est blandit, in bibendum neque auctor.</p>
    <p>Suspendisse potenti. Pellentesque consectetur, risus eu cursus interdum, enim eros dictum erat, sit amet accumsan arcu justo a erat.</p>
    <p>Fusce eu justo in orci sodales auctor. Proin vel tellus eu eros ultricies suscipit nec nec nunc.</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
